<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Async on Profile</title><link>https://bao2482003.github.io/22DTHC5-6_BaoDG_MBT/tags/async/</link><description>Recent content in Async on Profile</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 27 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://bao2482003.github.io/22DTHC5-6_BaoDG_MBT/tags/async/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>JavaScript: Async/Await và Xử Lý Bất Đồng Bộ</title><link>https://bao2482003.github.io/22DTHC5-6_BaoDG_MBT/posts/javascript-async-await/</link><pubDate>Sat, 27 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bao2482003.github.io/22DTHC5-6_BaoDG_MBT/posts/javascript-async-await/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="vấn-đề-với-callback-hell"&gt;Vấn đề với Callback Hell&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trước đây, xử lý bất đồng bộ trong JavaScript rất khó đọc:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getData&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMoreData&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMoreData&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMoreData&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;d&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;d&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="promise-giải-quyết-phần-nào"&gt;Promise giải quyết phần nào&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getData&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMoreData&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMoreData&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getMoreData&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;d&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;d&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; .&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="asyncawait---giải-pháp-tối-ưu"&gt;Async/Await - Giải pháp tối ưu&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Async/await giúp code bất đồng bộ trông như đồng bộ:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>